{
  "id": "rules_glossary/a/aspects",
  "lookup_group": "rules_glossary",
  "lookup_id": "aspects",
  "title": "Aspects",
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "img",
      "items": []
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "There are four aspects: Awareness, Fitness, Focus, and Spirit."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Your Ranger's aspects are printed on their aspect card."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "During"
        },
        {
          "type": "a",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Phase 4"
            }
          ],
          "link": {
            "id": "rules_glossary/p/phase_4_refresh",
            "anchor": "",
            "url": "/docs/rules_glossary/P/phase_4_refresh"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "of the"
        },
        {
          "type": "a",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "round"
            }
          ],
          "link": {
            "id": "rules_glossary/r/round",
            "anchor": "",
            "url": "/docs/rules_glossary/R/round"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": ", Refresh, add"
        },
        {
          "type": "a",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "energy"
            }
          ],
          "link": {
            "id": "rules_glossary/e/energy",
            "anchor": "",
            "url": "/docs/rules_glossary/E/energy"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "tokens to your energy pool until you have a number of each energy type equal to the corresponding aspect value. At this time, if you have"
        },
        {
          "type": "a",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "energy"
            }
          ],
          "link": {
            "id": "rules_glossary/e/energy",
            "anchor": "",
            "url": "/docs/rules_glossary/E/energy"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "tokens in excess of any of your aspect values, you must"
        },
        {
          "type": "a",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "discard"
            }
          ],
          "link": {
            "id": "rules_glossary/d/discard",
            "anchor": "",
            "url": "/docs/rules_glossary/D/discard"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "the excess tokens."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "During"
        },
        {
          "type": "a",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Phase 2"
            }
          ],
          "link": {
            "id": "rules_glossary/p/phase_2_ranger_turns",
            "anchor": "",
            "url": "/docs/rules_glossary/P/phase_2_ranger_turns"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "of the round, Ranger Turns, you can have any number of energy tokens in your energy pool. You are not limited by your aspect values in this way."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Your aspects determine which cards you are able to include in your deck. Each"
        },
        {
          "type": "a",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Ranger card"
            }
          ],
          "link": {
            "id": "rules_glossary/r/ranger_cards",
            "anchor": "",
            "url": "/docs/rules_glossary/R/ranger_cards"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "has an aspect requirement on the lefthand side of the card. You can only include a card in your deck if your corresponding aspect value is greater than or equal to the requirement."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Thematically, aspects represent your Ranger's inherent characteristics."
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "items": [],
  "url": "/docs/rules_glossary/A/aspects"
}